cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE

This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on generating misspelled Bengali words. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves analyzing patterns and generating rules, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of algorithms and analysis of data could also be relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
